## MCP Client Configuration

Add to your MCP client config (e.g. Claude Desktop `config.json`):

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{ plan.slug }}": {
{% if plan.transport == "stdio" %}
      "command": "uv",
      "args": ["run", "python", "server.py"]
{% else %}
      "url": "http://localhost:8000/mcp",
      "transport": "{{ plan.transport }}"
{% endif %}
    }
  }
}
```
